{"tid":593704,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"腦胃出問題 打嗝打唔停","createTime":"2018-03-15T08:13:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-15T13:33:33.000Z","uid":10958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"9447590383f7a548e5763c9f7818916497f8411f","tid":593704,"uid":10958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T08:13:35.000Z","msg":"<strong>腦胃出問題 打嗝打唔停</strong><br />\n<br />\n[img]<a href=\"https://resource01.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2025000/2029271/027_01_a_20180314_L.jpg[img][/img][/img]\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2025000%2F2029271%2F027_01_a_20180314_L.jpg%5Bimg%5D%5B%2Fimg%5D%5B%2Fimg%5D&d=TJ3MZuC4%2BvlQOXGaWtZ5AV0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=a8a6b348\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://resource01.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2025000/2029271/027_01_a_20180314_L.jpg[img][/img][/img]</a><br />\n<br />\n不論男女老幼都試過打嗝，雖然它一般只屬短暫性，但總令人感覺不舒服甚至尷尬。有腸胃肝臟專科醫生表示，如短暫性的打嗝毋須過慮，但若是長期打嗝就應要求醫，了解是否胃部甚至腦部健康出現問題。有中醫師亦指，如經常打嗝只是病徵，除或因胃部健康出現問題，也可能是因壓力所致。<br />\n<br />\n打足一兩日 宜及早求醫<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2025000/2029271/14JKA002__20180314_S.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2025000%2F2029271%2F14JKA002__20180314_S.jpg&h=e2ce9698&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n腸胃肝臟專科醫生呂恩妮表示，當橫隔膜肌肉出現抽搐便會出現打嗝，而打嗝的成因有不少，其中最普遍是因進食時太急促所致，「當食嘢食得好快吞埋啲空氣入去，就會刺激橫隔膜的肌肉抽搐，因而出現打嗝。此外，如果有嚴重咳嗽或有胃酸倒流，都會影響橫隔膜肌肉收縮而打嗝。」<br />\n<br />\n呂醫生續稱，除了上述原因，另外如受麻醉藥、類鴉片藥物等影響，也會令人較易打嗝；至於一些較罕見的情況，則是因長期病或手術性引起，例如有部分曾中風病人，其腦部負責控制橫隔膜的神經綫如受病情影響，便會較易出現打嗝，但這些情況並不普遍。<br />\n<br />\n打嗝時每每令人感到不舒服，如身處社交場合，不停打嗝更令人感到尷尬。呂醫生表示，打嗝一般只是幾分鐘甚至十多分鐘，期間亦可透過喝水及閉氣等方法使它停止，但如打嗝打足一兩日甚至更長時間仍未停，就可能是因胃部及腦部的健康出現問題，如出現此情況必須求醫了解原因，有需要時或要透過使用藥物作治療。<br />\n<br />\n食無定時壓力大 也會引發<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2025000/2029271/14JKA001__20180314_S.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2025000%2F2029271%2F14JKA001__20180314_S.jpg&h=4d67db52&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n註冊中醫師陳俊傑表示，打嗝即是呃逆、又稱為噦逆，中醫角度其原因是胃氣上逆，「胃氣本身宜降，但當胃的功能失調，胃部的氣會衝上橫隔膜，就會引起橫隔膜不正常抽動，因而打嗝。」<br />\n<br />\n此外，陳醫師指香港人常食無定時，嗜吃生冷食物，且愛不斷進食如零食等「垃圾食物」，這些不良飲食習慣除易傷脾胃，亦使胃部難有休息時間，正常運作功能勢受影響。此外，若生活上承受很大的壓力，休息不足，亦會令胃氣不順，令脾胃變得虛弱，當胃氣失調就會容易出現打嗝。<br />\n<br />\n他續指，如偶然打嗝問題不大，可按壓內關穴5分鐘左右緩解；至於平日就可用陳皮焗水飲用，以令脾胃平和；不過，如經常打嗝或某些日子突然多了嗝，就代表胃部健康或精神壓力方面可能出現問題，就需注意並尋找病源，不能輕視。<br />\n<br />\n編輯︰林子豐<br />\n<br />\n美術︰熊偉然<br />\n<br />\n記者︰蔡淑儀<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2025000/2029271/14JKA003__20180314_S.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2025000%2F2029271%2F14JKA003__20180314_S.jpg&h=87a9adde&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">進食時太急促是打嗝最常見的成因，但一般只維持幾分鐘至十多分鐘。（iStock）</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2025000/2029271/027_01_b_20180314_L.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2025000%2F2029271%2F027_01_b_20180314_L.jpg&h=84d6962f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2025000/2029271/027_01_c_20180314_L.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2025000%2F2029271%2F027_01_c_20180314_L.jpg&h=53341677&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://skypost.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2029271/%E8%85%A6%E8%83%83%E5%87%BA%E5%95%8F%E9%A1%8C%20%E6%89%93%E5%97%9D%E6%89%93%E5%94%94%E5%81%9C\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fskypost.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Farticle%2F2029271%2F%25E8%2585%25A6%25E8%2583%2583%25E5%2587%25BA%25E5%2595%258F%25E9%25A1%258C%2520%25E6%2589%2593%25E5%2597%259D%25E6%2589%2593%25E5%2594%2594%25E5%2581%259C&d=TJ3MZuC4%2BvlQOXGaWtZ5AV0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=0af6993c\" target=\"_blank\">https://skypost.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2029271/%E8%85%A6%E8%83%83%E5%87%BA%E5%95%8F%E9%A1%8C%20%E6%89%93%E5%97%9D%E6%89%93%E5%94%94%E5%81%9C</a>"},{"pid":"235c6443dee5b1757b995a14572b3b7bf17015fa","tid":593704,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T08:55:16.000Z","msg":"睇左：腦胃出問題 打J打唔停<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff72c218c6767bf693b31500d945758291d3a2b4","tid":593704,"uid":67500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T11:35:04.000Z","msg":"Milf<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78d366e689aacb5bc42a3b99c422030d7f26a47e","tid":593704,"uid":26711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T12:35:29.000Z","msg":"手足個腦都有問題？"},{"pid":"e47d7c92da75a8adadb1b331d2944049e56f178c","tid":593704,"uid":130545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T12:41:39.000Z","msg":"我係經常打果隻仲要好大聲<br />\n已經一年幾都係咁..<br />\n好想知如果係腦神經個話可以點醫？"},{"pid":"04c0b397de5d2723b4460583d2d1c12ad0efab32","tid":593704,"uid":63154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e47d7c92da75a8adadb1b331d2944049e56f178c","tid":593704,"uid":130545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T12:41:39.000Z","msg":"我係經常打果隻仲要好大聲<br />\n已經一年幾都係咁..<br />\n好想知如果係腦神經個話可以點醫？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T12:50:59.000Z","msg":"就算真係腦神經問題，都唔駛理，因為通常都冇得醫，無謂side錢，唔影響生活就算架啦"},{"pid":"e90c99b279f811a63fca75c275af50a27d5acfeb","tid":593704,"uid":130545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"reply